    • Method Detail

      • uiReadyMedicalAction

        public static MedicalActionBuilder uiReadyMedicalAction()
        Creates a new, ui ready, MedicalActionBuilder with the following fields set
        • Exposure - if an exposure is specified via onExposure or by using exposureBuilder.withMedicalAction then use the specified exposure. Otherwise a new ui ready medical details exposure is created.
        • ActionDate - set to a unique date before today
        • MedicalActionType - a randomly selected action type
          Returns:
          a new ui ready builder
